Properties

Uom

Gets/Sets the UomIdentifier which encodes the unit of measure (UOM) for the list of values.

[Required]
[JsonProperty("uom")]
public required UomIdentifier Uom { get; set; }

Property Value

UomIdentifier

A valid UomIdentifier, such as "m" for meters.

Remarks

This attribute is required and ensures that all values in the list are expressed in a consistent unit.

Values

Gets the ObservableCollection<T> with the measured values.

[JsonProperty("values")]
public ObservableCollection<double> Values { get; set; }

Property Value

ObservableCollection<double>

An ObservableCollection<T>.

Remarks

This is a list of double values representing quantities in the specified UOM.
